description: Roaming the Metro Detroit area, Beignets 2 Go provides great tasting beignets, prepared fresh with the highest quality of ingredients. Dedicated to serving the needs of customers each and every day, Beignets 2 Go takes pride in offering the best dessert experience on wheels. This food truck features delicious, hot, French pastries called beignets (BEN-YEY), which are doughnuts dusted with powdered sugar that are popular in New Orleans.
name: Beignets 2 Go
